-- query16
SELECT
 Count(DISTINCT cs_order_number) AS order_count ,
 Sum(cs_ext_ship_cost) AS total_shipping_cost ,
 Sum(cs_net_profit) AS total_net_profit
FROM catalog_sales cs1 ,
 date_dim ,
 customer_address ,
 call_center
WHERE Cast(d_date AS DATE) BETWEEN Cast('2002-3-01' AS DATE) AND (
 Cast('2002-5-01' AS DATE))
AND cs1.cs_ship_date_sk = d_date_sk
AND cs1.cs_ship_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
AND ca_state = 'IA'
AND cs1.cs_call_center_sk = cc_call_center_sk
AND cc_county IN ('Williamson County',
 'Williamson County',
 'Williamson County',
 'Williamson County',
 'Williamson County' )
AND EXISTS
 (
 SELECT tpc-ds-data-gen FROM catalog_sales cs2
 WHERE cs1.cs_order_number = cs2.cs_order_number
 AND cs1.cs_warehouse_sk <> cs2.cs_warehouse_sk)
AND NOT EXISTS
 (
 SELECT tpc-ds-data-gen FROM catalog_returns cr1
 WHERE cs1.cs_order_number = cr1.cr_order_number)
ORDER BY count(DISTINCT cs_order_number)
LIMIT 100;
